### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================================================
### AUTHENTICATION (Get Token First)
### ============================================================================

### Login as Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@greentech.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### ============================================================================
### EMPLOYEE LEADERBOARD
### ============================================================================

### Get Employee Leaderboard (Top 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/employees?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Employee Leaderboard for Specific Month
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/employees?month=11&year=2024&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Employee Leaderboard by Department
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/employees?department=Engineering&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get My Current Rank
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/my-rank
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### DEPARTMENT RANKINGS
### ============================================================================

### Get Department Rankings
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/departments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Department Rankings for Specific Month
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/departments?month=11&year=2024
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### COMPANY RANKINGS
### ============================================================================

### Get Company Rankings (Top 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/companies?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### ACHIEVEMENTS
### ============================================================================

### Get My Achievements
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/achievements/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Another Employee's Achievements (Admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/achievements/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### TRENDS & ANALYTICS
### ============================================================================

### Get Monthly Trends (Last 6 months)
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/trends?months=6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Monthly Trends (Last 12 months)
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/trends?months=12
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### PERFORMANCE COMPARISON
### ============================================================================

### Compare My Performance with Company Average
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/compare
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Compare My Performance for Specific Month
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/compare?month=11&year=2024
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Compare My Performance with Department
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/compare?department=Engineering
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}